{"tid":174213,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【劈價賣盤】印度籍商人劈價近三成賣灣仔酒店","createTime":"2017-03-26T15:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T00:13:07.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"755f4fa860dd995d5fec76a03258033ee7499da6","tid":174213,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T15:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/26/233638_b354b775e2faeb664506185000a5c2c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F26%2F233638_b354b775e2faeb664506185000a5c2c4.jpg&h=266e689f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印度籍商人2008年金融海嘯前席以2.6億元購入灣仔隆堡雅逸酒店，最近劈價近三成放售，叫價5億元，平均每間酒店房約625萬元，比同區酒店放盤平逾4成。<br />\n<br />\n美聯商業助理營業董事蔡永婷表示，灣仔摩理臣山道11號隆堡雅逸酒店，地盤面積1,621方呎，樓高23層，提供80間房間，每月收租約50萬元。業主原叫價7億元，最近調低叫價至5億元，減價2億元或28.6%，平均每間酒店房作價約625萬元。比較同區酒店低逾4成，例如摩理臣山道39號晉逸時代精品酒店提供93間房間，叫價10億元，平均每間房約1,075萬元。<br />\n<br />\n劈價雖狠，但原業主2008年2月以2.6億元購入，若以叫價沽出，賬面仍2.4億元。土地註冊處資料，原業主為力運香港有限公司，公司股東包括Dayaram Mukesh Harkishindas、Butani Papu Udharam及Kirpalani Ashok。據悉他們為印度籍商人，從事出口業務，包括服飾。他們曾短炒舖位，2013年曾以1.518億元購入尖沙嘴厚福街H8地舖。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56484126&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170326\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56484126%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170326&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=6ffb4c06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56484126%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170326&h=e3dcab8c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56484126&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170326</a>"},{"pid":"68b9569a55c8647623ea8666726aa0241f9957bb","tid":174213,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T16:00:17.00