09aa3e4a39a989841de100fe1b90b99b","tid":174213,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:38:44.000Z","msg":"咁似d 開高售價<br />\n 再折 話平左幾成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98652099de259c4d47e090a33f83903d318385a","tid":174213,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:41:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個月先租得50萬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一年先600萬。十年6000萬。仲未計管理，圍修，水電人工。有生之年都賺唔返</blockquote><br />\n你廿年內就過生?"},{"pid":"4f2ad3904851964d54940aff0730ab4fcdc8902f","tid":174213,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:42:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ba789e840d189695bb562a5d29bc237617ff032","tid":174213,"uid":42509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T11:30:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一個月先租得50萬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一年先600萬。十年6000萬。仲未計管理，圍修，水電人工。有生之年都賺唔返</blockquote><br />\n你廿年內就過生?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n二十年賺得返五億？你kai架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e925d26b433dd82deeee002d837338f7c1ae010","tid":174213,"uid":22481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T11:35:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2.6億購入，劈價三成買500,000,000？</blockquote><br />\n返小學讀書啦柒頭</blockquote><br />\n買同賣都打錯埋, 真係小學都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bff1911867fc27653bae9c05ebfe54825754895","tid":174213,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T11:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一個月先租得50萬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一年先600萬。十年6000萬。仲未計管理，圍修，水電人工。有生之年都賺唔返</blockquote><br />\n你廿年內就過生?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n二十年賺得返五億？你kai架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地收完租棟野仲可以賣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c9ac876df0236e5d9b8cc3604e32db9479fbdd","tid":174213,"uid":72304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:01:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一個月先租得50萬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一年先600萬。十年6000萬。仲未計管理，圍修，水電人工。有生之年都賺唔返</blockquote><br />\n可能買盈富，回報率仲高過佢<br />\n<br />\n未必志在長揸，可能志在短炒賺差價，2.4億買入，5億賣出，再加埋收租都有賺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓高23層，提供80間房間，每月收租約50萬元<br />\n<br />\n當你入住率5成長期租得40間房, 每間房每個月收入12,500, 每晚房租係417蚊<br />\n<br />\n照咁睇似係經營不善先得果月租50萬喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正常酒店你做到7成入住率, 灣仔區500蚊晚, 都應該有840k/month 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 月收租仲未計支出, 50萬扣埋極可能乜錢都無賺仲要蝕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb97aad2bf23e9ad7b99cb8a1a9adeff51fc0ff","tid":174213,"uid":42509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:02:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一個月先租得50萬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一年先600萬。十年6000萬。仲未計管理，圍修，水電人工。有生之年都賺唔返</blockquote><br />\n你廿年內就過生?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n二十年賺得返五億？你kai架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地收完租棟野仲可以賣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n賣家唔使講啦。2.6億買返黎放到5億唔計中間租金都賺左啦。鬼唔知咩。<br />\n<br />\n我講緊接貨個個呀。20年內點賺5億呀"},{"pid":"d38e2f5df7088b9b15d56512444e3b116bd1d076","tid":174213,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:06:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2.6億購入，劈價三成買500,000,000？</blockquote><br />\n返小學讀書啦柒頭</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad3691841b20c5cc73b19cecf800cf92bf57442","tid":174213,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:08:15.000Z","msg":"都賺呀"},{"pid":"e74cc21f6f4a32b9b1b38af6e415be90eb57894e","tid":174213,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T12:21:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2.6億購入，劈價三成買500,000,000？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n智障就返去讀特殊學校啦"}]}